<ul>
  <li>Connected directly to PLUS highway</li>
  <li>Paved, well-maintained roads</li>
  <li>Clear signage</li>
</ul>

<h3>Secondary Road Access (Good)</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Connected via main roads</li>
  <li>Mostly paved, some wear</li>
  <li>Acceptable for guests</li>
</ul>

<h2>Guest Booking Influence</h2>

<p>Our data shows:</p>
<ul>
  <li>67% ask about parking before booking</li>
  <li>45% express concern about road conditions</li>
  <li>28% cite accessibility as key factor</li>
</ul>

<h2>iHousing's Assessment</h2>

<p>Before you buy, we evaluate:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Drive from highway to property</li>
  <li>Check parking safety</li>
  <li>Test road conditions</li>
  <li>Assess rainy season access</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>WhatsApp iHousing today:</strong> Get location assessment for your property.</p>`;
---
<BlogPost
  title={title}
  description={description}
  image={image}
  date={date}
  category={category}
  language={language}
  content={content}
/>
